Still, you have a major problem by **using scriptlets in your JSP**. Refer to [How to avoid Java Code in JSP-Files?](https://stackoverflow.com/q/3177733/1065197) and start practicing [EL](https://stackoverflow.com/tags/el/info) and [JSTL](https://stackoverflow.com/tags/jstl/info) and focusing more on a MVC solution instead.

This line of yours:
    
    &lt;%@ page import=&quot;pageNumber.*, java.util.*, java.io.*&quot; %&gt;

Requires an `@` symbol before `%` like this:

    &lt;%@ page import=&quot;pageNumber.*, java.util.*, java.io.*&quot; @%&gt;

